import React from 'react';
import {StyleSheet, View} from 'react-native';
import {Dropdown, Icon, Nav, Sidenav} from 'rsuite';
import 'rsuite/dist/styles/rsuite-default.css';

const Mystyle={
  navwidth:{
     width:250
    },
  backgroundColor:{
    backgroundColor:'#white',

  }
}

function NavbarV(){
  return(
    <View style={StyleSheet.flatten([Mystyle.navwidth])}>
   <Sidenav style={StyleSheet.flatten([Mystyle.backgroundColor])} expanded={false} defaultOpenKeys={['2', '4']} activeKey="1">
      <Sidenav.Body >
        <Nav >

          <Nav.Item eventKey="1"   icon={<Icon icon="dashboard" size="lg"  style={{paddingLeft:"100px",paddingRight:"100px"}} />}>
            Operators
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="2" icon={<Icon icon="group" />}>
            Dashboard
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="3" icon={<Icon icon="mortar-board" />}>
            Students
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="4" icon={<Icon icon="lock" />}>
            Admins
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="5" icon={<Icon icon="universal-access" />}>
            Credentials
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="6" icon={<Icon icon="key" />}>
            Verifications
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item eventKey="7" icon={<Icon icon="link" />}>
            Networks
          </Nav.Item>

          <Dropdown
            eventKey="8"
            title="Apllications"
            icon={<Icon icon="gear-circle" />}
          >
            <Dropdown.Item eventKey="8-1">Applications</Dropdown.Item>
            <Dropdown.Item eventKey="8-2">Channels</Dropdown.Item>
            <Dropdown.Item eventKey="8-3">Versions</Dropdown.Item>
            <Dropdown.Menu eventKey="8-5" title="Custom Action">
              <Dropdown.Item eventKey="8-5-1">Action Name</Dropdown.Item>
              <Dropdown.Item eventKey="8-5-2">Action Params</Dropdown.Item>
            </Dropdown.Menu>
          </Dropdown>
        </Nav>
      </Sidenav.Body>
    </Sidenav>
  </View>
  )
}

export default NavbarV;
